meaning_str.bing:
num. 十四
n. 十四岁；十四的记号
网络. 第十四；十四个；第十四章

第十四；十四个；第十四章

十四；十四岁；十四个（人或物）；表示十四的符号；十四点钟

1.en: Fourteen-year-old Marlo had to move Clare's arms for her in the beginning, but now Clare follows part of the routine by herself.
1.cn: 开始14岁的玛洛必须扳着克莱尔的手做动作，现如今克莱尔自己能完成一部分动作了。

2.en: At the age of fourteen, a good sister saved me, I swear future will have the opportunity to help those who need help and the like!
2.cn: 十四岁时，一个好心的大姐救了我，我发誓将来有机会一定会帮助那些和一样需要帮助的人！

3.en: Fourteen of these "measured" rate rises were attributable to Greenspan and three to Bernanke, who replaced him in February 2006.
3.cn: 这些利率增长措施十四次是格林斯潘领导实施，三次由伯南克领导，伯南克于2006年1月顶替格林斯潘成为美联储主席。

0.cn: 十三.十四.十五.十六.十七.

1.cn: 十三，十四，十五，十六，十七。

2.en: Eleven, twelve, thirteen ,fourteen, fifteen, sixteen, seventeen, eighteen, nineteen, twenty.
2.cn: 十一，十二，十三，十四，十五，十六，十七，十八，十九，二十！

3.en: This is the ship that made the Kessel Run in 14 parsecs? Twelve! Fourteen.
3.cn: 这就是那艘只用十四秒差距完成科舍尔航程的飞船？十二秒！什么十四秒。

4.en: Travelling the eight hundred mile trip from Shanghai to Beijing used to take fourteen hours, now you can get there in just over five hours at speeds upwards of 180 miles per hour.
4.cn: 从上海到北京有一千两百多公里。过去需要十四个小时，现在你只需要五个多小时就能抵达，时速已达到两百九十公里。

6.en: Fourteen hundred species of fish live here, and a quarter of all marine species.
6.cn: 有1400种鱼类生活在这里，还有四分之一的海洋物种。

7.en: Really? How old? Fourteen and a half. You were the youngest person ever to win it.
7.cn: 真的吗？几岁？14岁半。那你"曾是"历史上年纪最小的获奖人。

8.en: But middle class wages during that same time period have gone up by only fourteen cents.
8.cn: 但中产阶级的工资在这一时期仅仅增长了14分钱。

9.en: Parking duty? Chief? Chief Bogo? Sir. You said there were fourteen missing mammal cases.
9.cn: 交通协管？局长？牛局长？长官，你说有14起哺乳动物失踪案。

10.en: Fourteen thousand and four, to be precise. My mother was approaching her ninety-first millennium when she passed.
10.cn: 确切的说，一万四千零四岁。我妈妈去世的时候已经快九万一千岁了。

11.en: A 25-year-old Harvard Law graduate took South Carolina State Senate District Fourteen by storm. His name was Francis J. Underwood.
11.cn: 25岁的哈佛法学院毕业生席卷了南卡罗莱纳州州参议院第14区，他的名字是弗兰西斯·J·安德伍德。

12.en: Easy for you to say, you already know what your kids names are going to be. You do? Yeah, I've had them picked out since I was fourteen.
12.cn: 你说的倒容易，你已经知道你的孩子要叫什么名字了。是吗？我14岁时就帮他们取好了名字。

13.en: Alright, alright, alright. It's been fourteen and a half minutes and you still have not said one word. Oh, god. Do something! Just make contact. Smile.
13.cn: 已过了14分30秒，你却连一字也没说，争气点，打破沉闷，微笑。
